[girl 1] Check it out! It looks
like Orimura and Dunois are
going to fight.

26
00:02:47,455 --> 00:02:51,958
[girl 2] Wow!
[girl 3] Dunois's personal
machine is called Rafale
Revive, right?

27
00:02:52,058 --> 00:02:55,594
[girl 4] It's a
second‐generation
type IS from France.

28
00:02:55,694 --> 00:02:57,228
