very simply, don't you?

48
00:04:17,278 --> 00:04:20,747
[Houki] Hmph! And you don't even
listen to any of my advice!

49
00:04:20,847 --> 00:04:23,449
[Rinin] And after I tried
to teach you so kindly too!

50
00:04:23,549 --> 00:04:26,918
[Cecilia] And what was wrong
with my very articulate
explanations?

51
00:04:27,018 --> 00:04:30,386
[Ichika] The thing is,
the Reiraku Byakuya is
an insane attack...

52
