are you okay?

107
00:07:21,161 --> 00:07:23,896
Yeah and thanks for saving me
earlier, by the way.

108
00:07:23,996 --> 00:07:25,997
I really owe you one for that.

109
00:07:29,666 --> 00:07:32,068
[Charles] Well, I'm heading back
to the room now.

110
00:07:32,168 --> 00:07:35,737
