Don't be like that!

118
00:07:54,582 --> 00:07:55,750
[screaming]

119
00:07:55,850 --> 00:07:57,817
[Charles] I have to go!
[Ichika] Charles?

120
00:08:00,285 --> 00:08:01,686
Huh...?

121
