[Chifuyu] Don't make me say the
same thing over and over again.

126
00:08:24,901 --> 00:08:26,669
I have my own role to play.

127
00:08:26,769 --> 00:08:28,236
That's all you need to know.

128
00:08:28,336 --> 00:08:30,638
[Laura] What kind of role could
you possibly have to play...

129
00:08:30,738 --> 00:08:32,239
