136
00:08:47,148 --> 00:08:50,450
they mistaken the IS for
some kind of extravagent
fashion accessory!

137
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:54,119
I find it unbelievable that you
could even give the time of day
to these people!

138
00:08:54,219 --> 00:08:56,954
I think I've heard more than
enough, little girl.

139
00:08:58,189 --> 00:09:01,324
You've grown up quite a bit
since I last saw you.

140
00:09:01,424 --> 00:09:05,494
But not enough to assume you're
the chosen one when you're
only fifteen.

141
00:09:05,594 --> 00:09:09,962
[Laura] I was just...
[Chifuyu] I'm a busy woman and
you need to get back to your
dorm, girl.

142
00:09:22,070 --> 00:09:24,839
[Chifuyu] Male student over
there, were you eavesdropping?

143
00:09:24,939 --> 00:09:27,173
Or indulging in some aberrant
sexual behavior?

144
00:09:27,273 --> 00:09:30,209
How can you say that, Chifuyu?
You're my sister for
cripes sake!

145
00:09:30,309 --> 00:09:32,977
At school, you will call
me Miss Orimura.

146
00:09:33,377 --> 00:09:34,678
Yes ma'am.

147
00:09:34,778 --> 00:09:36,913
You don't have time to waste
lurking in the bushes,

148
00:09:37,013 --> 00:09:38,447
