there training.

149
00:09:38,547 --> 00:09:40,415
At the rate you're going, you're
going to be defeated...

150
00:09:40,516 --> 00:09:42,950
in the first round of the next
month's tournament.

151
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:44,484
[Ichika] I know that.

152
00:09:44,584 --> 00:09:46,352
In that case, fine.

153
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,854
Hey, wait a second!

154
00:09:48,954 --> 00:09:52,723
I wanted to ask you something
about what Laura said to me
in class earlier...

155
00:09:52,823 --> 00:09:56,592
[Ichika] She said she doesn't
approve of me being
your brother.

156
00:09:56,692 --> 00:09:58,193
Was she talking about...

157
00:09:58,293 --> 00:09:59,728
the way you missed out
on the chance...

158
00:09:59,828 --> 00:10:01,629
to win the second championship
because of me‐

159
00:10:01,729 --> 00:10:03,163
[Chifuyu] That's all in
the past, kid.

160
00:10:03,263 --> 00:10:05,731
There's no need for you to
worry about it now.

161
00:10:06,265 --> 00:10:07,466
Later, 'kay?

162
00:10:14,037 --> 00:10:16,204
[Ichika] <i>It was the</i>
<i>2nd Mondo Grosso,</i>

163
00:10:16,304 --> 00:10:18,673
<i>the second IS world</i>
<i>championship...</i>

164
00:10:18,773 --> 00:10:22,375
<i>And on the day the final</i>
<i>match was supposed to</i>
<i>take place,</i>

165
00:10:22,475 --> 00:10:24,376
<i>someone kidnapped me.</i>

166
00:10:27,211 --> 00:10:31,147
<i>To this day, I still have</i>
<i>no idea why they did it.</i>

167
00:10:31,248 --> 00:10:34,015
<i>But I was detained</i>
<i>and imprisoned.</i>

168
00:10:36,584 --> 00:10:43,455
<i>And my big sister Chifuyu</i>
<i>abandoned the final match in</i>
<i>order to come and rescue me.</i>

169
00:10:43,555 --> 00:10:46,590
<i>So, my sister lost the</i>
<i>final match by default.</i>

170
00:10:46,690 --> 00:10:50,360
<i>No one had any doubt</i>
<i>that she was about to</i>
<i>win back‐to‐back victories,</i>

171
00:10:50,460 --> 00:10:53,595
<i>so it caused a controversy when</i>
<i>she pulled out of the match.</i>

172
00:10:53,695 --> 00:10:56,629
<i>And to top it off, in order to</i>
<i>repay the German Army...</i>

173
00:10:56,730 --> 00:11:00,299
