<i>about the location where I</i>
<i>was being held,</i>

174
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:06,336
<i>Chifuyu agreed to stay there</i>
<i>and serve as an instructor</i>
<i>for the German IS unit for</i>
<i>over a year.</i>

175
00:11:06,436 --> 00:11:09,137
<i>I felt as though it</i>
<i>was all my fault,</i>

176
00:11:09,237 --> 00:11:11,006
<i>like I was good‐for‐nothing...</i>

177
00:11:11,106 --> 00:11:14,308
