to be a guy?

208
00:13:40,700 --> 00:13:43,402
My family wanted me to do it.

209
00:13:43,502 --> 00:13:44,469
[Ichika] Your family?

210
00:13:44,569 --> 00:13:46,804
Oh, you mean your
family's corporation...

211
