214
00:13:54,976 --> 00:13:57,077
To be perfectly honest...

215
00:13:58,678 --> 00:14:01,113
I am not the child of his wife.

216
00:14:03,247 --> 00:14:06,683
[Charles] I was separated from
him for a very long time,

217
00:14:06,783 --> 00:14:09,685
