[Charles] Currently, IS research
is focusing on development of
the third‐generation type.

232
00:15:01,918 --> 00:15:05,786
I think the reason Miss Cecilia
and Miss Laura transferred to
this school...

233
00:15:05,886 --> 00:15:09,956
was because they needed
to collect data for
that development.

234
00:15:10,056 --> 00:15:15,026
The Dunois Corporation has
already begun developing
third‐generation models,

235
00:15:15,126 --> 00:15:16,860
but progress has been slow.

236
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:21,263
And at this rate, their
development permit is in
danger of being withdrawn.

237
00:15:21,363 --> 00:15:25,499
But what does any of that have
to do with you coming here and
pretending to be a boy?

238
00:15:25,599 --> 00:15:30,236
[Charles] It's simple.
I'm merely the
advertising platform
for attracting attention.

239
00:15:30,336 --> 00:15:33,371
As for this charade, it was felt
I had a better chance...

240
00:15:33,471 --> 00:15:36,706
of meeting you if I pretended
to be a boy.

241
00:15:36,806 --> 00:15:42,309
The hope was that I
could collect data on
your machine as well as you.

242
00:15:42,409 --> 00:15:44,111
[Charles] Basically, what they
asked me to do...

243
00:15:44,211 --> 00:15:46,346
was to come here and
steal your data...

244
00:15:46,446 --> 00:15:50,348
by pretending that I was a boy
named Charles.

245
00:15:53,383 --> 00:15:56,218
Now I feel a huge burden
has been lifted.

246
00:15:56,318 --> 00:15:58,487
Thank you for listening to me.

247
00:15:58,587 --> 00:16:02,322
And I am so very sorry about
lying to you all this time.

248
00:16:04,257 --> 00:16:06,559
[Ichika] But you never
wanted this, right?

249
00:16:07,259 --> 00:16:08,826
I mean, this entire plot.

250
00:16:08,926 --> 00:16:10,261
There's no way that you did!

251
00:16:10,361 --> 00:16:11,762
Uh, Ichika?

252
00:16:11,862 --> 00:16:14,497
Our parents are important or we
wouldn't be here without them,

253
00:16:14,597 --> 00:16:16,065
but even so...

254
00:16:16,165 --> 00:16:18,566
A parent can't just use a kid
as a tool like that!

255
00:16:18,666 --> 00:16:20,901
That's wrong in so many ways!

256
00:16:21,001 --> 00:16:22,402
[Charles] Ichika...

257
00:16:22,502 --> 00:16:25,904
[Ichika] My sister and I were
both abandoned as kids...

258
00:16:26,004 --> 00:16:27,905
so I know how you feel.

259
00:16:28,005 --> 00:16:31,841
The difference is that I have
no interest in ever seeing
them again.

260
00:16:31,941 --> 00:16:33,942
But you do.

261
00:16:34,042 --> 00:16:35,910
So, what are you going
to do now?

262
00:16:36,010 --> 00:16:37,411
What am I...?

263
00:16:38,512 --> 00:16:40,713
Now that you found out
I am a girl,

264
00:16:40,813 --> 00:16:44,015
I am sure I will be called
back to my home country.

265
00:16:44,115 --> 00:16:46,717
I don't really know
about the rest.

266
00:16:46,817 --> 00:16:50,052
Sent to jail, if I'm lucky.

267
00:16:50,152 --> 00:16:52,421
[Ichika] What if you just
stay here?
[Charles] What?

268
00:16:52,521 --> 00:16:55,089
You'll be fine as long as
I don't say anything right?

269
00:16:55,189 --> 00:16:57,224
And even if they do find out,
I'm sure your father...

270
00:16:57,324 --> 00:17:00,258
or his company can't do
anything about it at this point.

271
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:03,861
It's right here in the IS
Academy Special manual...

272
00:17:03,961 --> 00:17:07,597
All students of IS Academy are
under its exclusive control,

273
00:17:07,697 --> 00:17:11,733
and no nation, organization or
other group can interfere with
their attendance here.

274
00:17:11,833 --> 00:17:14,501
In other words, you'll be
safe for at least the
next three years...

275
00:17:14,601 --> 00:17:16,869
as long as you keep
attending this school.

276
00:17:16,969 --> 00:17:21,006
[Ichika] And with that
protection, you'll have
time to engineer a more
permanent solution.

277
00:17:21,106 --> 00:17:23,207
I can't believe you knew that.

278
00:17:23,307 --> 00:17:26,275
I mean there are fifty‐five
of those to remember.

279
00:17:26,375 --> 00:17:29,444
Well, it might not seem like it,
but I do study hard!

280
00:17:29,544 --> 00:17:30,712
[laughing]

281
00:17:31,545 --> 00:17:33,213
[Charles] Ichika...

282
00:17:35,415 --> 00:17:38,416
Thank you for covering for me.

283
00:17:38,517 --> 00:17:40,318
Well, no problem.

284
00:17:42,219 --> 00:17:45,687
[Ichika] Uh, your breast!
I can almost see your breast!

285
00:17:47,455 --> 00:17:51,525
Oh! Uh... does it
really bother you?

286
00:17:51,625 --> 00:17:53,392
Well of course they do!

287
00:17:55,293 --> 00:17:57,028
Would you like to see them?

288
00:17:57,128 --> 00:17:58,562
[Ichika] Say what?!

289
00:17:58,662 --> 00:17:59,730
You are a pervert.

290
00:17:59,830 --> 00:18:01,064
[Ichika] Me?! Who's a‐ what?!

291
00:18:01,164 --> 00:18:03,098
Where the hell did that
come from?!

292
00:18:04,199 --> 00:18:06,267
[Cecilia] Ichika,
are you in there?

293
00:18:06,367 --> 00:18:08,669
I noticed that you haven't
had dinner yet.

294
00:18:08,769 --> 00:18:10,370
Are you feeling ill?

295
00:18:14,805 --> 00:18:16,607
Ichika, I'm coming in.

296
00:18:17,907 --> 00:18:19,843
Oh, what are you doing
over there?

297
00:18:19,943 --> 00:18:22,010
N‐Nothing, it's just
that Charles...

298
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,345
told me that he might be coming
down with a cold,

299
00:18:23,445 --> 00:18:24,946
so I put a blanket on him.

300
00:18:25,046 --> 00:18:27,113
[Cecilia] Oh really?
[fake coughing]

301
00:18:27,213 --> 00:18:29,214
Dear, I'm sorry to hear that.

302
00:18:29,315 --> 00:18:32,250
Would it be all right with you
if I borrowed Ichika for a bit?

303
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,252
[fake coughing]
[Charles] Go ahead.

304
00:18:34,352 --> 00:18:37,354
Well it just so happens that I
haven't had my dinner either.

305
00:18:37,454 --> 00:18:39,121
Would you care to dine with me?

306
00:18:39,221 --> 00:18:41,389
Uh, sure?
[fake coughing]

307
00:18:41,489 --> 00:18:43,290
[Charles] Enjoy yourselves.
[giggling]

308
00:18:43,390 --> 00:18:45,225
[Cecilia] Let's be off then!
[Ichika] Hey...

309
00:18:47,126 --> 00:18:48,627
What are you doing?!

310
00:18:48,727 --> 00:18:51,963
We're on our way to dinner.
Just the two of us together.

311
00:18:52,063 --> 00:18:54,330
[Houki] But why do you have to
have your arm through his arm...

312
00:18:54,430 --> 00:18:56,131
and get so close to him
to do that?

313
00:18:56,231 --> 00:19:00,634
Oh, don't you know
that a gentleman is always
expected to escort a lady?

314
00:19:00,734 --> 00:19:04,136
Actually it feels more like
I'm being escorted...

315
00:19:04,237 --> 00:19:06,305
Then, I'm coming along
with you two!

316
00:19:06,405 --> 00:19:09,107
I didn't have enough at dinner
earlier, so I'm still hungry.

317
00:19:09,207 --> 00:19:14,277
Very well, but eating like that
is sure to put even more weight
on that boyish figure of yours.

318
00:19:14,377 --> 00:19:16,744
Hmph. Well that's none
of your business, is it?

319
00:19:16,844 --> 00:19:19,046
[Houki] We'll have some
sword practice later.

320
00:19:19,146 --> 00:19:21,047
That's a good way to burn
off calories!

321
00:19:21,147 --> 00:19:22,582
[Ichika] Ugh,
more with the hitting!

322
00:19:22,682 --> 00:19:25,484
Then it's settled.
Let's be off, shall we?

323
00:19:25,584 --> 00:19:27,918
Miss Houki, what do you think
you're playing at here?

324
00:19:28,019 --> 00:19:31,821
[Houki] You said a gentleman
is expected to escort a
lady, didn't you?

325
00:19:31,921 --> 00:19:32,989
[Ichika] Hold on, you two!

326
00:19:33,089 --> 00:19:34,723
It's really hard to
walk like this‐

327
00:19:34,823 --> 00:19:36,224
Owww!

328
00:19:36,324 --> 00:19:38,158
[Cecilia] Do you mean you don't
have anything else...

329
00:19:38,258 --> 00:19:39,559
to say about this situation?

330
00:19:39,659 --> 00:19:42,428
[Houki] Yes, such as how
deliriously happy you are,

331
00:19:42,528 --> 00:19:43,795
you lucky dog.

332
00:19:48,064 --> 00:19:49,965
[door opening and closing]

333
00:19:50,065 --> 00:19:51,766
[Ichika] Hey, it's me.

334
00:19:51,867 --> 00:19:52,834
I think...

335
00:19:52,934 --> 00:19:54,402
Uh, welcome back.

336
00:19:54,502 --> 00:19:56,737
Is there something wrong?

337
00:19:57,737 --> 00:19:59,505
Don't you worry about it.

338
00:19:59,605 --> 00:20:01,907
[Ichika] I brought some food
for you.

339
00:20:02,007 --> 00:20:04,542
Thank you, I am hungry.

340
00:20:08,177 --> 00:20:09,011
What's wrong?

341
00:20:09,111 --> 00:20:11,279
[Charles] Uh well...

342
00:20:15,816 --> 00:20:17,850
Oh, you can't use chopsticks?

343
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:20,218
I have been practicing,
but still...

344
00:20:20,318 --> 00:20:23,153
No problem, I'll just run back
and get you a fork, okay?

345
00:20:23,253 --> 00:20:25,522
Huh? No, that's okay.

346
00:20:25,622 --> 00:20:30,025
You know, you're going to have
to learn how to take advantage
of your roommate's kindness a
little better.

347
00:20:30,125 --> 00:20:33,393
[Ichika] What is it they say
about he who hesitates is lost?

348
00:20:34,393 --> 00:20:36,529
So, you take advantage of
me this time...

349
00:20:36,629 --> 00:20:39,864
And I'll take advantage of
you some other time, okay?

350
00:20:42,132 --> 00:20:45,800
[Charles] Well,
all right... I...

351
00:20:45,901 --> 00:20:47,301
[Ichika] Hm?

352
00:20:48,536 --> 00:20:50,671
Couldn't you just feed me?

353
00:20:53,239 --> 00:20:57,242
You said I could take advantage
of your kindness...

354
00:20:57,842 --> 00:20:59,209
[Charles] No?

355
00:21:01,444 --> 00:21:04,379
Okay! My word is my bond!

356
00:21:06,413 --> 00:21:09,182
Here comes the IS...

357
00:21:09,282 --> 00:21:11,116
Now say "ah"!

358
00:21:11,216 --> 00:21:12,684
Aah...

359
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:19,088
[Ichika] So, do you like it?

360
00:21:19,189 --> 00:21:20,556
Oh, very!

361
00:21:20,656 --> 00:21:23,191
That's good to hear!
More fish coming up!

362
00:21:23,291 --> 00:21:26,726
[Charles] Well, I think I want
to have some rice next.

363
00:21:26,826 --> 00:21:28,194
You want rice now?

364
00:21:28,294 --> 00:21:30,363
[Ichika] Here it comes!
Get ready!

365
00:21:31,163 --> 00:21:32,964
Hangar open! Say "ah"!

366
00:21:33,064 --> 00:21:34,465
[Charles] Aah!

367
00:21:35,632 --> 00:21:38,000
[Ichika] Oh, you got some
rice on your...

368
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:40,035
[Charles] Oh! Better get it.

369
00:21:40,135 --> 00:21:42,836
[Ichika] Okay, I guess I have
no choice...

370
00:21:49,341 --> 00:21:51,076
[Laura] Mentor...

371
00:21:51,176 --> 00:21:53,317
Your absolute and
incomparable strength...

372
00:21:53,417 --> 00:21:57,854
is a goal I seek. The very
reason for my continued
existence.

373
00:22:03,223 --> 00:22:05,191
And Ichika Orimura...

374
00:22:05,291 --> 00:22:08,660
The person who cast a stain upon
my mentor's name...

375
00:22:09,377 --> 00:22:10,618
I swear that...

376
00:22:10,718 --> 00:22:13,885
I will get rid of you by any
means necessary!

377
00:23:50,772 --> 00:23:53,072
[girl 1] Oh, my goodness, it
looks like there's a fight
in the arena!

378
00:23:54,739 --> 00:23:56,139
[girl 2] No way!
Who's fighting?

379
00:23:56,239 --> 00:23:58,306
[girl 3] It looks like one side
is the powerful duo...

380
00:23:58,406 --> 00:23:59,906
of Cecilia Alcott and Rinin Fan!

381
00:24:00,006 --> 00:24:02,172
[girl 1] And their opponent
is Laura Bodewig!

382
00:24:02,272 --> 00:24:05,106
[girl 2] Two against one?
That sounds like too much
of a handicap!

383
00:24:05,206 --> 00:24:07,539
[girl 3] Hang on, something
seems to be wrong!

384
00:24:07,639 --> 00:24:09,639
[girl 1] What?!

385
00:24:09,739 --> 00:24:12,172
[girl 3] The next episode,
"Blue Days ‐ Red Switch"

386
00:24:12,272 --> 00:24:16,906
You don't want to miss
the true power of the
third‐generation type IS!

